data.description: Downtown Jefferson, Jefferson City Schools!!! Step into this stunningly remodeled home, where sophistication meets functionality at every turn. This exquisite residence features high-end appliances and fixtures, and it includes the refrigerator and the washer and dryer, soft close cabinets, a gas stove with a pot filler, and a microwave hidden in the pantry, the kitchen is not only a chefas dream, but it is also a work of art! No expense was spared when this home was remodeled, notice fine details such as a light in every closet and above both showers, custom tile in the kitchen and bathrooms, custom shelving, offering a blend of comfort and style. Step outside to find a meticulously landscaped yard and a fully fenced backyard with two storage units. Seller is offering a one year HSA home warranty.
